Texts.Chs: 把 ^orange;遗传物质^reset;带给我。(位于^orange;科学前哨站^reset;)
Texts.Eng: Bring the ^orange;Genetic Material^reset; to me at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

Texts.Chs: 不仅是肉类，遗传物质来自许多物质。只需要记住，只要是生存着的细胞结构的生物，那么它里面很可能就会存在一些遗传物质。
Texts.Eng: Genetic material comes from many things, not just meat. Remember that if it is alive and full of cells, it just might give you some.

Texts.Chs: ^green;肉类^reset;既好吃又实用。把一些^green;肉^reset;拿去萃取，然后交5份萃取物给我。
Texts.Eng: ^green;Meat^reset; is both delicious and useful. Extract some ^green;meat^reset; and bring me 5 of the results.
